                <h4 class="card-title my-2">Enjoy the Vacations</h4>
                <img class="card-img img-fluid" src="~/Images/Tourism/4.jpg" />
                <p class="card-text my-2">We believe that in our holidays we need to refresh our minds and souls. Healthy tourism  is a real need in today's challenging society. </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-*">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
                <h4 class="card-title my-2">Dream, Explore, Discover</h4>
                <img class="card-img img-fluid" src="~/Images/Tourism/2.jpg" />
                <p class="card-text my-2">We want to change the way people think about travelling. Tourism and Travelling is like converting your dreams into reality and exploring new adventures.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-*">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
                <h4 class="card-title my-2">Customer Satisfaction</h4>
