        <div class="col-12 p-4 m-4 mx-auto" align="center">
            <h1 class="text-capitalize font-weight-bold">Our <span style="color: #9B5DE5">Motivation</span></h1>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-* px-5">
            <div class="card border-0">
                <div class="card-text">
                    <p style="line-height:2;">We are taking pride in making vacation planning as easy and valuable as possible. Top Bus Tours plays a unique role in building England tourism working with wide range of partners in U.K and worldwide.</p>
